"title": "4450: fruit",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4450: fruit",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Edible produce of trees, usually sweet and pleasant-tasting. The climate of the Near East is particularly suitable for a wide range of fruit and several varieties are mentioned in Scripture.</p>\n<h2>Apples</h2>\n<h3>Sweet, pleasant-tasting fruit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:3\">SNG 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:11\">PRO 25:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:5\">SNG 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song7:8\">SNG 7:8</a></p>\n<h3>Apple trees</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:12\">JOL 1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song2:3\">SNG 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song8:5\">SNG 8:5</a>DEU <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song32:10\">32:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:8\">PSA 17:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:2\">PRO 7:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech2:8\">ZEC 2:8</a></p>\n<h2>Dates</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:19\">2SA 6:19</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:3\">1CH 16:3</a></p>\n<h2>Figs</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:23\">NUM 13:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:5\">NUM 20:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:18-1Sam25:20\">1SA 25:18–25:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam30:11-1Sam30:12\">1SA 30:11–30:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:1\">2SA 16:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:40\">1CH 12:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:13\">MRK 11:13</a></p>\n<h2>Grapes</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:3-Deut32:14\">DEU 32:3–32:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:9-Gen40:11\">GEN 40:9–40:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:23-Num13:24\">NUM 13:23–13:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:5\">NUM 20:5</a></p>\n<h2>Melons</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:5\">NUM 11:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:8\">ISA 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:5\">JER 10:5</a></p>\n<h2>Pomegranates</h2>\n<h3>Pleasant-tasting fruit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:7-Deut8:8\">DEU 8:7–8:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:23\">NUM 13:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:5\">NUM 20:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song6:11\">SNG 6:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song7:12\">SNG 7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song8:2\">SNG 8:2</a></p>\n<h3>Pomegranate trees</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:2\">1SA 14:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:12\">JOL 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:19\">HAG 2:19</a>SNG <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag4:3\">4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:13\">SNG 4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song6:7\">SNG 6:7</a></p>\n<h3>Representations of pomegranates in the tabernacle and temple</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:16-2Kgs25:17\">2KI 25:16–25:17</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:20-Jer52:23\">JER 52:20–52:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:31-Exod28:35\">EXO 28:31–28:35</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:22-Exod39:26\">EXO 39:22–39:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:15-1Kgs7:20\">1KI 7:15–7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:40-1Kgs7:42\">1KI 7:40–7:42</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:11-2Chr4:13\">2CH 4:11–4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:16\">2CH 3:16</a></p>\n<h2>Fruit and the fall</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:12\">GEN 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:7\">GEN 3:1–3:7</a></p>\n<h2>General references to fruit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:1-Amos8:2\">AMO 8:1–8:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:11-Gen1:12\">GEN 1:11–1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:29\">GEN 1:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:23-Lev19:25\">LEV 19:23–19:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:5\">ECC 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek47:12\">EZK 47:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:1\">MIC 7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:1-Rev22:2\">REV 22:1–22:2</a></p>\n<h2>Fruit as a symbol of spiritual growth</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:10\">MAT 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:33\">MAT 12:33</a></p>",
